title: Vegan "Purity": Collaborating with Hunters to Save the Hunted, etc.
description:
A video addressed to the ways in which the "personal purity" paradigm can shape our engagement with political issues in veganism… although "political pragmatism" does not offer us any sort of easy alternative.

Usual disclaimer: IF I LOOK EXHAUSTED, IT'S BECAUSE I AM EXHAUSTED.  ;-)
